                <h2><i class="fas fa-trophy gold-icon"></i> The Bottom Line</h2>
                <p>Bro billionaire stocks can make you richer‚Äî<strong>if</strong> you execute perfectly. But perfect
                    execution is rare.</p>
                <p>Index funds will make you rich‚Äî<strong>if</strong> you give them time and stay invested.</p>
                <p>The hybrid approach gives you both: stability to sleep at night, and upside to change your life.</p>
                <p><strong>The winner?</strong> The strategy you can stick with for 20 years.</p>
